1
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,800
I went to pay the bill.

2
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:04,480
How is it? Does it hurt?

3
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:08,440
Now it's injury upon injury.

4
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:20,080
You won't faint anymore.

5
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,080
I'm cured.

6
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:34,920
You want to break up? Fine.

7
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,560
I thought I was cured

8
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,090
and no longer afraid of people.

9
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,560
But it turns out

10
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,840
I just like

11
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:53,640
spending every minute and every second with you.

12
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,840
It hurts.

13
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,160
Let's be in a real relationship.

14
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,440
Bai Tianyu.

15
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,400
I like you.

16
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,920
Can we be together?

17
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,530
Aunt, hurry up. It's this room.

18
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,079
Cousin.

19
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,800
How did you fall so badly?

20
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,560
Will you be disabled?

21
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,200
Don't curse our Su Wan.

22
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:01,680
Mom.

23
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,880
Doudou can't eat ice cream.

24
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,210
Otherwise, it will die.

25
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,720
Ever since Ye Tianyu came to our family,

26
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,200
your dad left,

27
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,400
and Doudou died.

28
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,760
I really don't know

29
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,760
what else will happen in the future.

30
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,240
I sympathize with him being an orphan,

31
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:19,720
but now,

32
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:22,579
I really don't dare to keep him in our house anymore.

33
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,840
So clumsy.

34
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,400
I knew

35
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,160
that sooner or later,

36
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,000
you would end up in the hospital.

37
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:36,160
That's because my cousin is unlucky

38
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,160
and ran into a jinx.

39
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,680
And this is?

40
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:51,079
A friend.

41
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:51,720
You two... You...

42
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,440
Cousin.

43
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,040
Tianyu.

44
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,680
We...

45
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,170
I'll answer you.

46
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,399
My answer is no.

47
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:18,740
I'll leave now.

48
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,010
What did you do to Su Wan?

49
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,320
None of your business.

50
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,600
You made her cry.

51
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,400
How is it none of my business?

52
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,000
I grew up with her,

53
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,770
and I've never seen her cry.

54
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,280
What exactly did you do to her?

55
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:57,340
I thought she was too noisy, so I left.

56
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,560
Is that weird?

57
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,000
Do you think I'm an idiot?

58
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,200
She is

59
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:03,120
so weird and extremely annoying,

60
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,320
always messing things up.

61
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,520
Always throwing tantrums.

62
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,120
I can't even coax her enough.

63
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,250
She's so clingy.

64
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,480
But she only clings to you.

65
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,560
Don't take it for granted.

66
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,180
Did I ask her to cling to me?

67
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,000
Bai Tianyu.

68
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:31,000
How could self-centered people like you

69
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,200
ever consider

70
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,600
what others want or don't want?

71
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,920
Have fun yourselves.

72
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,100
I'm out of here.

73
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:50,960
Bai Tianyu.

74
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,800
You are a jinx.

75
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,560
You bastard, Bai Tianyu!

76
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:58,120
My sister hasn't been doing well since she met you.

77
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:00,650
Do you think you are good enough for my sister?

78
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,640
What?

79
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,320
Bai Tianyu is your childhood

80
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,760
sweetheart, Ye Tianyu?

81
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,440
And he is the only person

82
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,440
you've ever liked since childhood.

83
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,640
Oh my god, this is too romantic!

84
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,520
Please get married right now.

85
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,040
But I confessed,

86
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,160
and he rejected me.

87
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,040
You confessed,

88
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,920
and failed?

89
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,650
Why did I miss so much information?

90
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,600
But even a blind person can see

91
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,600
that he likes you.

92
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,000
Him?

93
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,640
Why are you here?

94
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,440
I know Tianyu rejected you.

95
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,260
But no matter what,

96
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:52,000
I should still come to visit.

97
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,840
Your brother is ridiculous,

98
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,080
but as a sister, you are quite sensible.

99
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:59,680
But she is definitely your future sister-in-law.

100
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,360
Who can say for sure when it comes to love?

101
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,820
Tianyu also said he would always protect me.

102
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:09,810
Why did you come here today?

103
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,500
To make her mad on purpose?

104
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,480
Of course not.

105
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,360
I was afraid she would be sad,

106
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,360
so I came especially to comfort her.

107
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,660
The three of us were adopted by my father.

108
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,880
We've shared joys and sorrows for over a decade.

109
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,640
Of course we don't want to be separated.

110
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,960
Please understand.

111
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:30,000
Tianyu saying such things while you're in the hospital

112
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,440
is definitely inappropriate.

113
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,000
I apologize to you on his behalf.

114
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,920
Who are you to apologize for him?

115
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,540
Please get out.

116
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,159
You are not welcome here.

117
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,080
I'll be going now.

118
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,320
What a jerk.
